    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The motivation for writing this is that there aren‚Äôt many blogs and articles out there with these compact visualisations (if you do know of any, please share them with me). So I decided to write one for our reference. For this purpose, I have read the papers and the code (mostly from TensorFlow and Keras) to come up with these vizzes.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
