    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Paper: <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1409.4842" target="_self">Going Deeper with Convolutions</a></li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Authors: Christian Szegedy, Wei Liu, Yangqing Jia, Pierre Sermanet, Scott Reed, Dragomir Anguelov, Dumitru Erhan, Vincent Vanhoucke, Andrew Rabinovich. Google, University of Michigan, University of North Carolina</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Published in: 2015 IEEE Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
