    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>‚≠êÔ∏è What‚Äôs novel?</strong></p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ol><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><em>Popularised</em> skip connections (they weren‚Äôt the first to use skip connections).</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Designing even deeper CNNs (up to 152 layers) without compromising the model‚Äôs generalisation power</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Among the first to use batch normalisation.</li></ol></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
