            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>üìùPublication</strong></p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Paper: <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385" target="_self">Deep Residual Learning for Image Recognition</a></li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Authors: Kaiming He, Xiangyu Zhang, Shaoqing Ren, Jian Sun. Microsoft</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Published in: 2016 IEEE Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
